  <title>geur</title>
  <p><strong>geur</strong> is an <a href="?xx=adjectives/adjectives">adjective</a>, with the basic meaning <en>bitter, sharp</en>.</p>
  <hr/>
  <h5><m>geur</m> as compounding prefix</h5>
  <p>As a <a href="?xx=verbs/compound_verbs">verb-compounding</a> prefix –</p>
  <ul>
    <li><i>amhairc</i> <en>look, see</en> ⇒ <m>geur-amhairc</m> <en>stare</en></li>
    <li><i>lean</i> <en>follow, pursue</en> ⇒ <m>geur-lean</m> <en>persecute</en></li>
    <li><i>sgrùd</i> <en>inspect, examine</en> ⇒ <m>geur-sgrùd</m> <en>pore</en></li>
  </ul>
  
